messages.message: When logged in using my personal email account, the “Provide Feedback” option defaults to the primary account in my Chrome session

Don't think we have much control over the email that shows here since it's from your browser cookies. The email showed here is also only used to sync your responses. But when you fill the form and click share e-mail you'll be see your logged in email prefilled. cc: @Junwon Jang
